          If you need to host any of your own projects, you can help us out by using our Digital Ocean affiliate link when you sign up:
          = link_to 'https://m.do.co/c/411ca1d7b00c', 'https://m.do.co/c/411ca1d7b00c'
          = image_tag('logos/do_logo_white.png', class: "img img-responsive footer-logo")
